## ğŸ“‚ Dataset
The dataset contains labeled SMS messages classified as spam or ham.

## âš™ï¸ How It Works
1. Text messages are converted into numerical features using CountVectorizer.
2. A Logistic Regression model is trained on the data.
3. The model predicts whether a new SMS is spam or not.

